WEBVTT

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:32.816
Only one crew had ever
pulled this off before.

00:00:32.840 --> 00:00:37.216
PN: And I still remember
when we actually were in space,

00:00:37.240 --> 00:00:40.776
just about to capture the thing,

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:43.456
and Cady had set up everything
and I was near her

00:00:43.480 --> 00:00:45.536
and we had the control
center on the radio.

00:00:45.560 --> 00:00:50.496
I was the one talking on the radio
and she was the one moving the arm,

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:53.096
and you know, we agreed, OK, we are ready.

00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:54.336
(Voices over the radio)

00:00:54.360 --> 00:00:57.736
AG: Paolo says it's like driving
your car at 300 miles an hour

00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:01.096
and trying to match the speed
of the car next to you precisely